14
00:04:19,833 --> 00:04:21,411
Give me a kiss.

15
00:04:22,294 --> 00:04:24,168
I'll talk to you later.

16
00:04:27,592 --> 00:04:29,252
Excuse me.

17
00:04:30,053 --> 00:04:31,761
Oh, excuse me...

18
00:04:31,971 --> 00:04:34,260
...when is somebody
gonna clean this off?

19
00:04:37,269 --> 00:04:39,807
And the Y?
The Y. We talked about this.

20
00:04:40,022 --> 00:04:43,438
It's an I in "happiness."
There's no Y in "happiness." It's an I.

21
00:04:45,736 --> 00:04:47,610
I'm Chris Gardner.

22
00:04:48,030 --> 00:04:51,115
I met my father for the first time
when I was 28 years old.

23
00:04:51,909 --> 00:04:53,569
And I made up my mind
as a young kid...

24
00:04:53,786 --> 00:04:55,280
... that when I had children...

25
00:04:55,496 --> 00:04:58,830
... my children were gonna know
who their father was.

26
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:03,462
This is part of my life story.

27
00:05:04,256 --> 00:05:07,625
This part is called "Riding the Bus."

28
