It's a time machine, isn't it?

30
00:05:19,438 --> 00:05:21,016
Seems like a time machine.

31
00:05:21,232 --> 00:05:24,316
That seems like a time machine.
It's a time machine. Take me with you.

32
00:05:24,527 --> 00:05:25,725
This machine...

33
00:05:26,196 --> 00:05:27,441
... this machine on my lap...

34
00:05:27,655 --> 00:05:29,613
This guy, he has a time machine.

35
00:05:29,824 --> 00:05:32,861
He travels in the past
with this machine and...

36
00:05:33,078 --> 00:05:35,320
- it is not a time machine.

37
00:05:35,872 --> 00:05:38,494
It's a portable
bone-density scanner.

38
00:05:39,334 --> 00:05:41,956
A medical device I sell for a living.

39
00:05:42,171 --> 00:05:44,662
Thank you for the opportunity
to discuss it with you.

40
00:05:44,882 --> 00:05:46,958
- I appreciate it.
- We just don't need it, Chris.

41
00:05:47,176 --> 00:05:48,920
It's unnecessary and expensive.

42
00:05:49,137 --> 00:05:51,260
- Well, maybe next...
- Thank you.

43
00:05:52,348 --> 00:05:57,426
It gave a slightly denser picture
than an x-ray for twice the money.

