when you're always in a rush.

57
00:06:37,772 --> 00:06:39,645
Thanks anyway. Very much.

58
00:06:39,857 --> 00:06:42,775
- Maybe next quarter.
- It's possible.

59
00:06:43,653 --> 00:06:49,193
I needed to sell at least two scanners
a month for rent and daycare.

60
00:06:50,076 --> 00:06:51,405
I'd have to sell one more...

61
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:55,404
... to pay off all of those tickets
under my windshield wiper.

62
00:07:02,214 --> 00:07:04,207
The problem is...

63
